</section>
<section>
<title>Documentation des champs</title>
<anchor xml:id="_struct_tag_def_1ab2ab707c2832eb3cd8776c3134b29b1d"/><section>
    <title>bit_pos_a</title>
<indexterm><primary>bit_pos_a</primary><secondary>TagDef</secondary></indexterm>
<indexterm><primary>TagDef</primary><secondary>bit_pos_a</secondary></indexterm>
<para><computeroutput>uint8_t bit_pos_a</computeroutput></para>
<para>Position du premier bit (de gauche à droite). exemple x0000000 serras 0 et 0x000000 seras 1 </para>
</section>
<anchor xml:id="_struct_tag_def_1a315b71fd9f91bd21c82164e006859ede"/><section>
    <title>bit_pos_b</title>
<indexterm><primary>bit_pos_b</primary><secondary>TagDef</secondary></indexterm>
<indexterm><primary>TagDef</primary><secondary>bit_pos_b</secondary></indexterm>
<para><computeroutput>uint8_t bit_pos_b</computeroutput></para>
<para>Position du premier bit (de la deuxième partie en cas d&apos;une valeurs entre 9 et 16 bits. 0 sinon) (de gauche à droite). exemple x0000000 serras 0 et 0x000000 seras 1 </para>
</section>
<anchor xml:id="_struct_tag_def_1a985f815d0edbf8a411fbf325a30baec8"/><section>
    <title>byte_idx_a</title>
<indexterm><primary>byte_idx_a</primary><secondary>TagDef</secondary></indexterm>
<indexterm><primary>TagDef</primary><secondary>byte_idx_a</secondary></indexterm>
<para><computeroutput>int8_t byte_idx_a</computeroutput></para>
<para>Index du byte (0 à 7), -1 si non utilisé </para>
</section>
<anchor xml:id="_struct_tag_def_1a1368f5414ba506dc1626d65a1083dc92"/><section>
    <title>byte_idx_b</title>
<indexterm><primary>byte_idx_b</primary><secondary>TagDef</secondary></indexterm>
<indexterm><primary>TagDef</primary><secondary>byte_idx_b</secondary></indexterm>
<para><computeroutput>int8_t byte_idx_b</computeroutput></para>
<para>Deuxième index pour les variables 16 bits, sinon -1 </para>
</section>
<anchor xml:id="_struct_tag_def_1a894ffee63faf79f0877a12c871a18b3a"/><section>
    <title>n_bits</title>
<indexterm><primary>n_bits</primary><secondary>TagDef</secondary></indexterm>
<indexterm><primary>TagDef</primary><secondary>n_bits</secondary></indexterm>
<para><computeroutput>uint8_t n_bits</computeroutput></para>
<para>Taille de la valeur (peux être 1, 3, 4, 8, ou 16. si 0, le tag n&apos;ais juste pas encore utilisé) </para>
</section>
<anchor xml:id="_struct_tag_def_1a5365d3ceaa5fb559687e0d26268ca709"/><section>
    <title>name</title>
<indexterm><primary>name</primary><secondary>TagDef</secondary></indexterm>
<indexterm><primary>TagDef</primary><secondary>name</secondary></indexterm>
<para><computeroutput>char name[<link linkend="_config__value_8h_1ada71b9f258860d58a86ab220bfce6bf4">MAX_TAG_NAME_LEN</link>]</computeroutput></para>
<para>Nom du tag (il dois être unique et être d&apos;une longueur inférieur à la longueur maximal spécifier par MAX_TAG_NAME_LEN) </para>
</section>
